data.title: What does Oui Oui mean in French?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 58): Oui Oui in French is the quintessential way of saying "Yes, yes," with an air of enthusiastic agreement or confirmation. It's the kind of response you'd give when someone asks if you're up for a night out and you're feeling particularly ready for some fun.
